        <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden mt-3"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] pr-8 text-left">What is a chattel mortgage?</h3><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] flex-shrink-0 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary><div class="p-6 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100"><p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed">A chattel mortgage is a business vehicle loan where you own the vehicle from day one and the lender holds a mortgage over it. You make regular repayments plus an optional balloon payment at the end. Interest, depreciation, and GST are all deductible.</p></div></details>
        <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden mt-3"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] pr-8 text-left">Do I need an ABN for business car finance?</h3><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] flex-shrink-0 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary><div class="p-6 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100"><p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed">An ABN is typically required and should be registered for at least 6-12 months. Some lenders prefer 24+ months. If you are a salaried employee wanting tax benefits, a novated lease through your employer is the equivalent option.</p></div></details>
        <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden mt-3"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] pr-8 text-left">Can I include a balloon payment?</h3><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] flex-shrink-0 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary><div class="p-6 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100"><p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed">Yes. A balloon payment reduces regular repayments and can help business cash flow. At the end of the term, you pay the balloon, refinance it, or trade the vehicle. Balloon percentages vary by lender and term length.</p></div></details>
